1.An Array is just a list of values.
2.Index: Starts with O.
3.Arrays are used for storing multiple values in a single variable

* Position = index + 1
* index = position - 1


* Syntax
       Type of array                   element type
            ⬆   array variable name         ⬆  length
            ⬆          ⬆                   ⬆    ⬆
           int[]      myInts      =      new int [10];

